### General Checklist
- [ ] I have added unit tests that prove my changes should work.
- [ ] I have successfully run tests locally.
- [ ] I have added proper doc comments to newly introduced functions.
- [ ] I have updated documentation (internal and external) to reflect my changes.
- [ ] I have pulled in the latest changes from master.
- [ ] I have run `gofmt -l -w .` on the project.
- [ ] I have successfully run `golangci-lint` locally.
- [ ] I have spent some time looking over the full diff before creating this PR.
- [ ] I have added the license to new source code files

If you cannot tick an item, please describe why.

